@sen3942   On the theory of descent with modification, the great law of the long enduring, but not immutable, succession of the same types within the same areas, is at once explained, for the inhabitants of each quarter of the world will obviously tend to leave in that quarter, during the next succeeding period of time, closely allied though in some degree modified descendants.

